<p rend="chapter">Mahāpadhānadīpanīgāthā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="111"><hi rend="paranum">111</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Orohitotohitapāpadhammo,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Channena sa channahayena gantvā;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Anomatīramhi anomasatto,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Anomapabbajjamupāgato so.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="112"><hi rend="paranum">112</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Nirāmisaṃ pītisukhaṃ anūpamaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Anūpiye ambavane alattha;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Sarūpasobhāya virūpasobhaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Sarājikaṃ rājagahaṃ karittha.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="113"><hi rend="paranum">113</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Tato aḷāra ūdakatāpasānaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Jhānenasantuṭṭhamano vihāya;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Mahāpadhānāya uruvelabhūmiṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Gato sikhappattamakāsi dukkaraṃ.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="114"><hi rend="paranum">114</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Na kāmato nevatidukkaramhi,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Sabbaññutā sijjhati majjhimāya;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Ñatvāna taṃ pubbaguṇopaladdhaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Dhammaṃ samānetumagā subodhiṃ.</p>
</body>
